    <note>Fan(2) Wenlian [30104] He moved to Beijing at age 35 and set up business, which apparently included construction and money-lending (but the text is not completely clear to us), and made a fortune. The funerary inscription specifies that his ancestor Bin [30106] was truly (shi 實) a 14th generation descendant of Fan Zhongyan. Zhu Yun, WJ, 13.256-257. 《清代人物生卒年表》定其生卒年為康熙34年~乾隆22年。 【參考《清代人物生卒年表》#14049.】</note>
